OL,3,CMan charged after #1 million suspected
OL,4,Ccocaine seized
OL,6,FA man has been charged after around #1
OL,7,Fmillion worth of suspected cocaine was
OL,8,Ffound in Co Tyrone.
OL,10,FThe 30-year-old was arrested in the
OL,11,FCookstown area on Friday.
OL,13,FPolice made the discovery following
OL,14,Fthe search of a property in the
OL,15,FDungannon area.
OL,17,FIt comes following the forensic
OL,18,Fexamination of two mobile phone
OL,19,Fdevices seized by officers when a
OL,20,Fvehicle was stopped in the Markethill
OL,21,Farea of Co Armagh in January.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
