OL,3,CMan charged after #1 million suspected
OL,4,Ccocaine seized
OL,6,FThe man has been charged with being
OL,7,Fconcerned in the supply of Class A
OL,8,Fcontrolled drugs, possessing a Class A
OL,9,Fdrug with intent to supply and being
OL,10,Fconcerned in the supply of Class B
OL,11,Fcontrolled drugs.
OL,13,FHe has also been charged with
OL,14,Fpossessing criminal property,
OL,15,Ftransferring criminal property, making
OL,16,Findecent images of children,
OL,17,Fpossessing indecent images of children
OL,18,Fand attempting to pay for sexual
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
